column120:
2pcs bottle and 4pcs cups samples were sent out to client by UPS#1ZF4Y7200499125982 on Sep 15th

Bottle: one piece with 2-lines frame, one piece with 1-line frame
cup: cream white and super white material, fake gold and real gold rim.

waiting for PAT to choose the final version

2023/10/20:
Pat think last sample color too dark, we prepare 8 new colors for selection, and Pat choose 5, under preparing new samples, version 1 color with 3 kinds of decal, and version 2-5 colors with one decal. Will be ready before Oct 30th, then customer can check them during this visit.
cups need matching version.

2023/10/24:
first improved samples are ready, Pat want to further change decal file, and make golden label on the neck to be 3D effect. Under further checking.
